data.description: Merry Christmas!!! Move in ready house in a wonderful area in the country in South Florence! 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on the ground floor. Bonus Room and bath upstairs. Beautiful front door, nice foyer and formal dining room. Site built cabinets. Kitchen has new granite tops and tile backsplashes. Good closet space in all bedrooms. Master bath has a double vanity, jetted tub, separate 4' shower, and toilet room with extra large cabinet over the toilet. Most of the house has fresh paint. Carpet and downstairs heat pump replaced in 2020. Water heater and microwave replaced in 2022. Wooded land- house sits on 1.57 acres and has a workshop with sheds attached. Workshop is 20"8" x 24". sheds are 18'- 4" x 39' Power and water at the workshop. Separate entrance from the street to the shop area. Note that workshop was moved from another site- we do not know the age of the main Leonard metal building. House has an attached 24 x 24 garage.  Great neighbors and NO HOA!! Listing Agent has ownership in property.
